title: Picasso On Art - A Selection of Views (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
Picasso On Art: A Selection of Views
Viking Press | 1972 | ISBN: 0670553271 | English | 224 pages | PDF | 30.3 MB

An anthology of Pablo Picasso's statements about art. An engaging, if not wholly cohesive, account of Picasso's sayoing and writings about art, but more. The strength of the book comes when he speaks on art. The ancilliary issues that come up serve to round out the figure of Picasso more, but may not quite be the art treatise you're looking for
